Class SnakeNode

java.lang.Object
  SnakeNode

public class SnakeNode
extends java.lang.Object

SnakeNode is a Node object used by SnakeTree Each node contains a Snake object which can be resolved through getSnake()

Version:
1.0
Author:
Niall Deasy
